openBliSSART depends on the following libraries:

- Poco Enterprise v1.3.6+ (incl. support for SQLite), http://pocoproject.org
- Simple Direct Media Layer, http://libsdl.org
- SDL_sound, http://icculus.org/SDL_sound
- Qt 4.4.3+, http://www.qtsoftware.com
- Fastest Fourier Transform in the West, http://www.fftw.org

Additionaly, performance can be vastly improved by installing the `Automatically
Tuned Linear Algebra Software' package, available at http://www.netlib.org/atlas.
